info.author: Hsiaoming Yang
classifiers: Topic :: Software Development :: Libraries :: Python Modules
info.name: OpenCC
info.summary: A ctypes-based OpenCC converter for Chinese.

vulnerabilities.details: Open Chinese Convert (OpenCC) 1.0.5 allows attackers to cause a denial of service (segmentation fault) because BinaryDict::NewFromFile in BinaryDict.cpp may have out-of-bounds keyOffset and valueOffset values via a crafted .ocd file.
